Diamond::

She slithered around in the vents, looking for Vamprah.  She knew how 
to hunt her pray, but she had never hunted a bot with instincts like 
her own before. She had to make her mind think as her prey.  She 
flicked her tongue and tasted the air around her. She was getting 
closer to her prey.
